snippet.title: Wanba Warriors - PC & Nintendo Switch™ Announce Trailer (2020)
snippet.description:
Step into the absurd world of calligraphy combat and prepare to lay the smackdown upon all who dare to oppose you, dishing out damage with your chosen ink brush of brutality!

Wanba Warriors available on PC and Nintendo Switch™ in 2020.

Download the demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1021770/Wanba_Warriors/
